elem_dict.key: 1299_823_351_63_This guide will show you how to build a slat-style toy box that can be adapted to all kinds of storage around your home. Substitute treated wood and exterior fasteners and it’s a deck box. Make it without the lid for a planter. Use a different paint scheme and it fits into the mud room.
